             was indicted for <rs id="t18090111-83-off492" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090111-83-off492" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090111-83-off492" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18090111-83-cd493" type="crimeDate">15th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090111-83-off492 t18090111-83-cd493"></join>, a copper, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090111-83-victim891" type="victimName">
                           Chambers 
                           Ions
                        <interp inst="t18090111-83-victim891" type="surname" value="Ions"></interp>
